item.title: EP 155 - Was Bigfoot Abducted By Aliens?
item.itunes:title: Was Bigfoot Abducted By Aliens?
item.description:
Today we look at a mysterious death and then take a drive down a dark, foggy road as we explore the alien sighting known as the Bosak Encounter.

 

When a man stumbles into a police station and talks of beings on the walls stalking him, the police call an ambulance for a drug overdose. When the ambulance reaches the hospital 5 minutes later he is found beaten into a coma. Was he really being stalked by a paranormal force?

And then we take a look at the “Bosak Encounter.” What did William Bosak really see on a lonely road one night? Did he see an alien piloting a ship or is the answer more sinister than that?
